T*
() Tj
T*
(The combined score uses a 0.58/0.42 heuristic/ML split because the rules layer is more) Tj
T*
(directly explainable and should remain slightly dominant, while ML still has enough) Tj
T*
(weight to move borderline cases and catch multivariate oddities. The thresholds are) Tj
T*
(conservative guardrails, not learned cutoffs. The same 0.62 heuristic and 0.90 ML) Tj
T*
(agreement thresholds used in suppression are also reported separately so blind spots are) Tj
T*
(visible:) Tj
